		 DisplayName: This should be unique for all integrations that you have in the same environment (Test/Prod) so that you can tell them apart in the list of services 
					  While French language (xml:lang="fr") is currently not supported, it is advised to include the correct application name in French to reduce the need for your application 
					  to resubmit a new metadata file should French become required
		 Description: A description is not presently required but may be leveraged in future releases
	- ICAM-CODE-REQUIRED-->	 
	<md:Extensions>
		<mdui:UIInfo>
			<mdui:DisplayName xml:lang="en">DPS RP Simulator 01</mdui:DisplayName> 
			<mdui:DisplayName xml:lang="fr">DPS RP Simulator 01 Fr</mdui:DisplayName>
			<mdui:Description xml:lang="en">Online tool for interacting with DPS</mdui:Description>
			<mdui:Description xml:lang="fr">Online tool for interacting with DPS FR</mdui:Description>
		</mdui:UIInfo>
	</md:Extensions>
	
